- Hey, you got a loosie?

19:53.501 --> 19:54.499
- What?

19:54.500 --> 19:55.667
- Loosie, loosie.

19:55.708 --> 19:57.166
- Yeah, how'd you know?

19:57.167 --> 19:58.166
- What?

19:58.167 --> 19:59.542
- My name.
Lucy.

20:02.917 --> 20:05.374
- Psychic, I guess.

20:05.375 --> 20:06.417
- Hmm.

22:23.292 --> 22:24.667
- All right, all right,
all right.

22:29.917 --> 22:31.957
Your father's debt?

22:31.958 --> 22:34.583
Now it's your debt.

22:34.625 --> 22:37.208
From now on, you work for me.

23:13.875 --> 23:16.208
- Who am I?

23:16.250 --> 23:18.542
Who am I?

23:18.583 --> 23:20.917
Detective Bobby Correlli,
that's who I am.

23:20.958 --> 23:22.167
Right here.

23:24.083 --> 23:25.458
I see you.
What are you, a squirrel?

23:25.459 --> 23:28.291
Stop in the name of the law!

23:28.292 --> 23:29.542
- Hey, Bobby.

23:29.583 --> 23:30.750
Shut up!

23:30.792 --> 23:32.792
- Take you downtown,
and not for a drink either.

23:34.792 --> 23:38.583
- <i>Alex Rodriguez hits one
deep to left.</i>

23:45.125 --> 23:47.583
- Plate glass window I like it.

23:48.375 --> 23:50.000
Very Dirty Harry.

23:50.792 --> 23:53.542
- Listen, it was you.

23:53.583 --> 23:56.041
You said whatever it takes.

23:56.042 --> 23:57.667
- Thanks, Pete.

23:57.708 --> 23:59.375
That's what I like about you,
Sully.

23:59.417 --> 24:01.457
Always do everything
just the way you want,

24:01.458 --> 24:03.167
never give a shit
what anyone thinks.

24:04.792 --> 24:07.166
- Well, why should I stop now?

24:07.167 --> 24:08.542
It's my life.
It's what I do.

24:08.583 --> 24:09.542
What else am I gonna do?

24:09.583 --> 24:12.083
I'm not qualified
for anything else.

24:12.125 --> 24:13.417
- So what's next?

24:13.458 --> 24:15.957
- What's next?

24:15.958 --> 24:18.667
I'm gonna get my badge back,

24:18.708 --> 24:20.292
even if I have to
kill that little prick.

24:25.583 --> 24:27.624
Hey, good morning.

24:27.625 --> 24:28.750
- Who the hell are you?

24:32.875 --> 24:36.458
- Um, I'm Carl.

24:37.292 --> 24:40.166
- Oh, Carl.

24:40.167 --> 24:41.167
Ma!

24:42.333 --> 24:43.417
Ma!

24:43.458 --> 24:45.125
- Oh, Bobby I thought
you'd be at work by now.

24:45.126 --> 24:47.000
- Who the hell is this guy?

24:47.042 --> 24:48.498
- Carl.
- No, I got that.

24:48.499 --> 24:50.708
What the hell is Carl
doing here, in my bathrobe?

24:50.750 --> 24:51.708
- You didn't tell him.

24:51.750 --> 24:53.832
- I didn't get a chance.
I didn't get a chance.

24:53.833 --> 24:56.083
- Okay, so, Bob, I'm a...

24:56.125 --> 24:57.708
I'm a friend of your mother's.

24:57.750 --> 24:59.333
- He's a friend of mine
from bingo.

24:59.334 --> 25:00.833
- Wait a minute.

25:00.875 --> 25:02.708
Did this guy?
Did the two of you...

25:02.750 --> 25:03.708
Ah.

25:03.750 --> 25:04.917
- It's not what you think,
Bobby.

25:04.958 --> 25:06.125
We've been friends a long time.

25:06.126 --> 25:09.125
I didn't want to tell you,
but I think it's time.

25:09.167 --> 25:10.166
Yeah.

25:10.167 --> 25:11.542
Carl's asked me
to move in with him.

25:11.583 --> 25:13.166
It's not what you think.

25:13.167 --> 25:15.166
- What?
I'm gonna kill this guy.

25:15.167 --> 25:16.583
- He's funny.
He's an ex-Marine.

25:24.625 --> 25:27.333
- What happened?

25:27.375 --> 25:30.250
You look like the walking dead.

25:30.292 --> 25:32.792
- Well, death would be
a welcome relief

25:32.833 --> 25:34.750
compared to the world
of shit I live in right now.

25:34.792 --> 25:37.375
- Talk to me.
I got your back.

25:37.417 --> 25:38.417
Tell me.

25:40.542 --> 25:42.042
- I got a girl pregnant.

25:42.083 --> 25:43.042
- Ooh.

25:46.042 --> 25:48.417
- Yeah.
- Whoa.

25:48.458 --> 25:51.958
- That's funny.
Laugh it up.

25:52.000 --> 25:54.957
- Yeah, I got your back.

25:54.958 --> 25:57.500
Way back, way, way back.

25:59.208 --> 26:01.125
Like, Toledo back.

26:03.000 --> 26:05.667
- Thanks.

26:05.708 --> 26:08.332
I'm so screwed.

26:08.333 --> 26:09.332
- Let's see.

26:09.333 --> 26:10.332
- Ah!

26:10.333 --> 26:11.833
- She do that?
She punch you?

26:11.875 --> 26:14.957
- No, I fell down the stairs.

26:14.958 --> 26:16.666
- All right.

26:16.667 --> 26:18.667
What's she gonna do?
She gonna keep the kid?

26:20.333 --> 26:22.957
- I don't know.
That option never came up.

26:22.958 --> 26:28.374
- Why would she want to keep
a baby without a father?

26:28.375 --> 26:30.125
Especially your baby.

26:32.167 --> 26:33.667
Why don't you just give her
some money,

26:33.708 --> 26:35.042
tell her to get rid of it?

26:37.208 --> 26:40.500
You're gonna be up to your neck
in dirty diapers.

26:40.542 --> 26:43.875
Listen to me.
Like a mission to the moon.

26:44.375 --> 26:45.375
Abort.

26:52.750 --> 26:55.417
- Hey, listen, do you know
where I can find Lucy?

26:55.458 --> 26:57.083
- Who's asking?

26:57.125 --> 26:58.625
- Me.

26:58.667 --> 27:00.457
- Who are you?

27:00.458 --> 27:02.833
- I'm a friend of hers
from childhood.

27:02.875 --> 27:04.167
- Ah, you know her from Ohio.

27:04.168 --> 27:05.500
- Yeah.

27:05.542 --> 27:06.875
- She grew up in Texas, jerkoff.

27:06.917 --> 27:09.000
Look, just go away.

27:09.042 --> 27:10.167
- Does she still work here?

27:10.208 --> 27:11.625
I just want to talk to her,
okay?

27:11.626 --> 27:13.791
- Yeah, you and half of the guys
in the bar.

27:13.792 --> 27:16.250
Beat it before I beat you.

27:16.292 --> 27:18.167
- Wow, did you just
come up with that yourself?

27:22.792 --> 27:23.750
Whoa, Lucy!
Lucy!

27:23.792 --> 27:24.750
Lucy!

27:24.792 --> 27:25.750
- You know this guy?
- No.

27:25.792 --> 27:26.750
- Lucy, it's me!

27:26.792 --> 27:28.208
- Stay away from her!

27:47.417 --> 27:49.583
- Get out of here!

27:49.625 --> 27:51.000
- Okay.
- What?

27:51.042 --> 27:52.583
No, wait, wait!

27:52.625 --> 27:54.417
Not you.

28:01.250 --> 28:02.833
- What are you doing here?

28:05.458 --> 28:08.583
- I'm sorry about the...
you know.

28:08.625 --> 28:11.542
I just...

28:11.583 --> 28:13.583
I mean, I was a little
in shook when you...

28:17.958 --> 28:20.583
I mean, you tell a guy
something like that, it's...

28:25.417 --> 28:27.250
So you... you want to keep it?

28:29.167 --> 28:32.208
- Do I want to keep it?

28:32.250 --> 28:35.124
It's not a stray dog, you know.

28:35.125 --> 28:37.333
- No, I know.
I just... I'm just saying.

28:37.375 --> 28:39.457
- What?
What are you saying?

28:39.458 --> 28:43.208
I'm listening to you,
but you're not saying anything.

28:43.250 --> 28:45.375
If you don't want
to have the baby,

28:45.417 --> 28:48.124
I'll help out, you know,
with the money.

28:48.125 --> 28:51.500
- Gee, what a stand-up guy.

28:51.542 --> 28:53.041
- What do you want from me?

28:53.042 --> 28:54.333
- I don't want
anything from you.

28:54.334 --> 28:57.583
You came here
to see me, remember?

28:57.625 --> 29:01.417
- I don't know
why you want to have a baby.

29:01.458 --> 29:03.290
Why do you want to bring a baby
into this world

29:03.291 --> 29:05.708
with a shit father who doesn't
want anything to do with it

29:05.750 --> 29:07.583
and a mother who can't afford
to take care of it?

29:07.625 --> 29:09.667
I mean...

29:12.375 --> 29:15.332
I'm tryin' to help you out
here, okay?

29:15.333 --> 29:16.917
- You've already done enough.
Thanks.

29:16.958 --> 29:17.958
- I can't talk to you.

29:18.000 --> 29:20.000
You just want to get smart
all the time and walk away.

29:20.042 --> 29:21.040
- If I was smart,

29:21.041 --> 29:22.708
I wouldn't have talked to you
to begin with,

29:22.750 --> 29:23.833
and I just would have
walked away.

29:23.875 --> 29:25.333
- See, that's what
I'm talking about.

29:25.334 --> 29:27.500
I'm trying to do my part here,
okay?

29:30.917 --> 29:34.792
I want to find a good doctor,
and I want to pay for it.

29:37.708 --> 29:39.042
So what do you say?

29:40.958 --> 29:42.167
- I say you're an asshole.

29:47.042 --> 29:48.625
But I'll think about it.

29:51.542 --> 29:52.875
- Wait.

29:55.333 --> 29:57.167
How do I get ahold of you?

30:00.417 --> 30:02.167
- Call me here.

30:02.208 --> 30:04.417
I'm livin' out of Gomer's
back office.

30:15.458 --> 30:17.833
- How much?

30:17.875 --> 30:21.624
No, I don't have insurance.

30:21.625 --> 30:23.167
I don't want a free clinic okay?

30:23.208 --> 30:25.375
I want to pay for it.

30:25.417 --> 30:27.625
No, I realize that, but...

30:28.833 --> 30:30.583
Okay, well, what if I paid cash?

30:30.625 --> 30:32.250
I mean, can we work a deal
or something?

30:32.292 --> 30:34.000
Hello?
Hello?

30:43.958 --> 30:46.333
- I just came by
to get the rest of my things.

30:48.958 --> 30:50.625
Bobby, can you just
say something?

30:50.626 --> 30:52.499
- Or what?

30:52.500 --> 30:53.833
You gonna have your boyfriend
beat me up?

30:53.875 --> 30:57.125
- He's a good man.
He needs me.

30:58.125 --> 31:00.332
- What about me, Ma?

31:00.333 --> 31:03.000
I need you.

31:03.042 --> 31:04.832
- No, you don't.

31:04.833 --> 31:06.791
You're taking care of me.

31:06.792 --> 31:08.792
I don't want you
to have to take care of me.

31:08.833 --> 31:10.917
With Carl,
we take care of each other.

31:10.958 --> 31:12.166
- Oh, yeah?

31:12.167 --> 31:14.333
Is that the arrangement you made
with your bingo buddy?

31:14.334 --> 31:15.832
- I love him, Bobby.

31:15.833 --> 31:18.000
Not the way I loved your father

31:18.042 --> 31:20.417
and not the way I love you.

31:20.458 --> 31:21.458
It's a different love.

31:22.792 --> 31:24.583
Maybe someday
you'll meet somebody,

31:24.625 --> 31:27.457
and you'll understand.

31:27.458 --> 31:29.624
You'll know.

31:29.625 --> 31:31.667
I got to go.

31:31.708 --> 31:34.666
Look, he wants to invite you
to dinner tomorrow night.

31:34.667 --> 31:37.333
Start fresh.

31:37.375 --> 31:38.750
Here's the number.

31:41.292 --> 31:43.750
I'm happy, Bobby.

31:43.792 --> 31:45.292
Can't you be happy for me?

31:53.958 --> 31:56.875
- Hey.

31:56.917 --> 31:59.332
Turn the iron setting down.

31:59.333 --> 32:01.000
Don't burn all his shirts
like you do mine.

32:15.833 --> 32:18.208
Hey, Jax.

32:18.250 --> 32:19.708
No, no, I can't today.

32:19.750 --> 32:21.333
I got to take care
of some stuff.

32:23.708 --> 32:24.707
- Bobby.

32:24.708 --> 32:26.207
Bobby Corelli.

32:26.208 --> 32:27.957
That's you, right?

32:27.958 --> 32:29.957
- What?
- Is that your name?

32:29.958 --> 32:31.375
You live here?
- Who?

32:31.417 --> 32:32.375
- You, Bobby.

32:32.417 --> 32:33.375
- Me?
I'm Tommy.

32:33.417 --> 32:34.375
- Tommy.

32:34.417 --> 32:35.375
- Tommy.
I'm just...

32:35.417 --> 32:36.375
I was visiting my aunt.

32:36.417 --> 32:37.750
- You don't live here?
- No.

32:37.792 --> 32:39.165
- Hey, Bobby, how's it going?

32:39.166 --> 32:40.667
I hear your mother's
getting married.

32:40.708 --> 32:41.917
Congratulations.

32:57.625 --> 32:59.500
- They got me, Jax.

32:59.542 --> 33:00.542
They got me.

33:00.583 --> 33:02.208
I don't know how they got me,
but they got me.

33:02.250 --> 33:03.208
- Who?
Who got you?

33:03.250 --> 33:04.290
- The cops.
The cops got me.

33:04.291 --> 33:06.208
They were all over my apartment
like a bees' nest.

33:06.250 --> 33:07.208
How did they get my name?

33:07.250 --> 33:08.208
- I don't know.

33:08.250 --> 33:09.290
I have no idea how they know.

33:09.291 --> 33:11.290
Maybe it was your little
girlfriend ratted you out.

33:11.291 --> 33:12.623
- She doesn't know what I do.

33:12.624 --> 33:13.790
- They follow you here?

33:13.791 --> 33:15.083
- No.
- How do you know?

33:15.125 --> 33:16.708
- You're fine, okay?

33:18.292 --> 33:21.124
- What are you gonna do?
- I don't know.

33:21.125 --> 33:22.123
I mean, I got to lay low.

33:22.124 --> 33:23.790
That's what I got to do.
Just got to lay low.

33:23.791 --> 33:25.125
- You find a place
to do that thing?

33:25.126 --> 33:27.124
- Yeah, Elmsview Hospital.

33:27.125 --> 33:29.000
I was born there,
so it must be good, right?

33:29.042 --> 33:31.750
- Must be terrific.
Look how you turned out.

33:31.792 --> 33:33.498
I need, like, a hundred bucks
or something.

33:33.499 --> 33:34.623
I got to stay at a motel.

33:34.624 --> 33:36.042
I got nowhere to go.
- Get out of here.

33:36.083 --> 33:38.042
- Give me a hundred bucks.
Where am I supposed to go?

33:38.083 --> 33:39.250
I don't got nothing, all right?

33:39.292 --> 33:40.583
Nothing for you.
- I'm not joking.

33:40.625 --> 33:41.583
I got nowhere to go.

33:41.625 --> 33:43.375
- No, I'm not gonna
give you nothing.

33:43.417 --> 33:44.458
- Are you kidding me?

33:46.750 --> 33:48.542
Prick!
You think I need you?

33:48.583 --> 33:50.167
I can just go pick
a couple of wallets.

33:50.208 --> 33:52.499
Hey, hey, hey,
you got 20 bucks?

33:52.500 --> 33:53.499
No?

33:53.500 --> 33:56.124
What is wrong with this kid?

33:56.125 --> 33:58.542
- Hey, Bobby.

33:58.583 --> 34:00.292
If I were you,
I'd stay off the subway.

34:00.293 --> 34:01.292
Take a taxi.

34:01.333 --> 34:02.667
- Yeah, thanks.

34:29.125 --> 34:32.291
Hey. Hey, Carl.
It's Bobby.

34:32.292 --> 34:34.875
Bobby, the guy
you punched in the face.

34:34.917 --> 34:39.042
Yeah, is...
is my mother there?

34:39.083 --> 34:40.498
She's asleep?
Okay.

34:40.500 --> 34:42.750
No, no, I didn't realize
what time it was.

34:42.792 --> 34:44.750
Just tell her I'll
see you guys tomorrow.

34:44.792 --> 34:46.791
Okay?
Yeah.

34:46.792 --> 34:47.875
No, I'm fine.

34:47.917 --> 34:49.667
Thanks, bye.

35:13.833 --> 35:15.499
Lucy

35:15.500 --> 35:16.583
Lucy.

35:20.042 --> 35:21.624
- Why are you whispering?

35:21.625 --> 35:23.333
If you're gonna pound
on the door like that,

35:23.334 --> 35:25.083
you might as well be screamin'.

35:25.125 --> 35:26.083
- I came to tell you

35:26.125 --> 35:29.042
that we have an appointment
tomorrow at 2:00,

35:29.083 --> 35:31.333
so if that works for you...

35:32.917 --> 35:35.375
- Well, uh...

35:35.417 --> 35:37.542
It's 3:00 in the morning, so...

35:37.583 --> 35:40.667
I'll see you in about 11 hours.

35:41.167 --> 35:42.666
Next time, try calling.

35:42.667 --> 35:44.500
Oh, wait, you don't do that.

35:46.792 --> 35:48.167
- I had a rough night.

35:48.208 --> 35:50.250
Maybe I can come in
for a second,

35:50.292 --> 35:51.292
for a drink or something.

35:51.333 --> 35:54.417
- In case you haven't noticed,
we're closed.

35:54.458 --> 35:55.875
- Can I just come in
for a minute,

35:55.917 --> 35:57.457
one minute?

35:57.458 --> 35:59.500
I...

35:59.542 --> 36:03.124
I have nowhere else to go.

36:03.125 --> 36:04.917
Please.

36:07.958 --> 36:08.958
- For a minute.

36:21.417 --> 36:23.957
- You got a cigarette?

36:23.958 --> 36:25.625
- Pregnant women don't smoke.

36:33.292 --> 36:34.667
You still want that drink?

36:34.668 --> 36:37.042
- Yeah.
Scotch, thanks.

36:43.167 --> 36:45.250
- You want to talk about it?

36:45.292 --> 36:46.583
- About what?

36:46.625 --> 36:48.750
About whatever's
got you worn slick.

36:50.708 --> 36:53.875
- Worn slick?
What is that, Texas slang?

36:54.833 --> 36:56.375
- How do you know
I'm from Texas?

36:56.417 --> 36:57.667
- I know a few things.

37:01.375 --> 37:04.375
- Then tell me,
Mr. Know-a-Few Things,

37:04.417 --> 37:05.708
what's got you pounding
on my door

37:05.750 --> 37:07.542
in the middle of the night?

37:14.583 --> 37:16.042
- I got evicted.

37:18.417 --> 37:20.833
- Okay.

37:35.458 --> 37:36.958
- Can I ask you a question?

37:41.667 --> 37:44.667
That Fred Flintstone guy
your boyfriend?

37:44.708 --> 37:46.624
- Why?
Are you jealous?

37:46.625 --> 37:49.375
- Curious.

37:49.417 --> 37:51.750
- No, he's not.

37:51.792 --> 37:53.791
I mean, he used to be.

37:53.792 --> 37:56.083
He, um...

37:56.125 --> 37:58.583
He just looks out for me now.

37:58.625 --> 38:01.583
Protective older brother.

38:01.625 --> 38:02.833
In fact, he'd probably kill you

38:02.875 --> 38:04.875
if he knew you were here
right now,

38:04.917 --> 38:08.667
especially if he knew you were
the one that knocked me up.

38:08.708 --> 38:10.208
- He knows about...

38:11.958 --> 38:13.375
- Yeah.

38:18.250 --> 38:19.791
Why are you so curious
about him?

38:19.792 --> 38:21.042
- I don't know.

38:21.083 --> 38:23.457
Just, you know,

38:23.458 --> 38:25.208
he's a lot different than me,
right?

38:25.250 --> 38:27.707
So I was just wondering,

38:27.708 --> 38:30.542
that night, you know, you...

38:30.583 --> 38:32.625
I mean, if that's the type
you like then why...

38:38.083 --> 38:39.583
Forget it.

38:40.833 --> 38:43.500
- You asking me why I went home
with you that night?

38:45.958 --> 38:47.333
- Yeah.

38:53.083 --> 38:55.375
- I've been asking myself that
every day for three months.

39:06.458 --> 39:08.375
It was your eyes.

39:08.417 --> 39:09.791
- My eyes?

39:09.792 --> 39:11.124
- Yeah.

39:11.125 --> 39:12.999
Yeah.

39:13.000 --> 39:14.208
I liked your eyes.

39:14.250 --> 39:16.750
You had really kind eyes.

39:17.750 --> 39:20.167
It kind of reminded me
of my father's.

39:20.208 --> 39:22.458
- So you went home with me
because I had nice eyes.

39:22.459 --> 39:23.708
- Kind eyes.

39:25.750 --> 39:29.542
Plus, you know,
I liked talking to you.

39:29.583 --> 39:32.167
I thought you were funny
and nice,

39:32.208 --> 39:34.917
and you had a great ass.

39:40.542 --> 39:42.875
I let you walk me home,
didn't I?

39:42.917 --> 39:44.667
- Yeah.

39:44.708 --> 39:46.166
Yeah.

39:46.167 --> 39:49.917
- And then when we
got to my apartment,

39:49.958 --> 39:51.500
you didn't even try anything.

39:51.542 --> 39:57.291
You just smiled and thanked me
for a great time

39:57.292 --> 39:58.457
and said...

39:58.458 --> 39:59.500
- "Good night."

40:03.292 --> 40:04.250
- And I don't know;

40:04.292 --> 40:08.000
I guess I just didn't want
the night to end.

