58:55.292 --> 58:57.457
- Thanks, Mom.

58:57.458 --> 59:00.167
- Lucy's a professional
photographer.

59:00.208 --> 59:01.583
- Oh, no.

59:01.625 --> 59:03.833
- Is that right?

59:03.875 --> 59:05.957
- Mostly freelance.

59:05.958 --> 59:08.332
But right now, I'm working
in a bar part-time.

59:08.333 --> 59:09.958
You know, it's not much,

59:10.000 --> 59:12.667
but at least
it's an honest living.

59:14.208 --> 59:15.167
- You're right about that.

59:15.208 --> 59:17.083
Rita said you were from Texas.

59:17.125 --> 59:18.624
- Mm-hmm.

59:18.625 --> 59:20.500
Yeah, I'm actually
heading back this Saturday.

59:20.542 --> 59:22.499
- Wow, that's too bad.

59:22.500 --> 59:24.333
Yeah, I think I'm gonna,
you know,

59:24.375 --> 59:26.166
move back in with my sister,

59:26.167 --> 59:27.165
you know, work at a...

59:27.166 --> 59:28.958
at a photography studio
shooting portraits.

59:28.959 --> 59:31.000
That sort of thing.

59:35.583 --> 59:38.000
- And you were planning
on telling me when?

59:38.042 --> 59:41.333
- Well, I wasn't really planning
anything with you.

59:43.625 --> 59:44.667
- How's the lasagna?

59:44.708 --> 59:46.499
- It's delicious.

59:46.500 --> 59:47.500
- Wonderful.

59:51.292 --> 59:52.291
Excuse me.

59:52.292 --> 59:53.667
- Do you need to use
the ladies' room?

59:53.708 --> 59:54.791
- No.

59:54.792 --> 59:56.292
- We don't got a ladies' room.

59:56.333 --> 59:57.500
Grampie's only got a bathroom.

59:59.250 --> 01:00:02.000
- Lucy, are you okay?

01:00:02.042 --> 01:00:03.000
What's the matter?

01:00:03.042 --> 01:00:04.000
Hey, hey!

01:00:04.042 --> 01:00:05.167
- Call 911!
- Breathe.

01:00:07.125 --> 01:00:09.167
- I'm not going into labor,
you moron.

01:00:09.208 --> 01:00:10.957
I'm only three months pregnant!

01:00:10.958 --> 01:00:12.167
- Bobby!

01:00:12.208 --> 01:00:14.417
- Ma...

01:00:14.458 --> 01:00:16.458
Oh, shit.

01:00:19.000 --> 01:00:23.917
- Why didn't you tell me, Bobby?

01:00:23.958 --> 01:00:25.667
- I didn't want
to worry you, Ma.

01:00:25.708 --> 01:00:27.000
- What worry me?

01:00:27.001 --> 01:00:29.333
Why would havin'
a grandkid worry me?

01:00:31.250 --> 01:00:32.958
Does she want to keep it?

01:00:35.583 --> 01:00:36.625
- I don't know.

01:00:39.625 --> 01:00:40.625
- Do you love her?

01:00:45.542 --> 01:00:46.500
- I don't know, Mom.

01:00:46.542 --> 01:00:50.250
I mean, I don't know
what love is.

01:00:50.292 --> 01:00:52.957
How do you...
how do you know?

01:00:52.958 --> 01:00:55.000
- Well, when she said
she was leaving on Saturday,

01:00:55.042 --> 01:00:57.499
how'd that make you feel?

01:00:57.500 --> 01:00:59.750
- Sick.

01:00:59.792 --> 01:01:01.456
- And when we were on our way
to the hospital,

01:01:01.457 --> 01:01:02.750
how did you feel?

01:01:05.417 --> 01:01:07.708
Sometimes it takes
almost losing what we have

01:01:07.750 --> 01:01:09.792
to make us realize
how lucky we are to have it.

01:01:12.792 --> 01:01:13.792
Dr. Phil.

01:01:17.792 --> 01:01:19.250
I'm gonna get going.

01:01:19.292 --> 01:01:20.833
I'll leave you two alone.

01:01:42.792 --> 01:01:45.124
- Hey.

01:01:45.125 --> 01:01:46.667
- Hi.

01:01:49.958 --> 01:01:52.333
- The doctors said
you're gonna be okay.

01:01:52.375 --> 01:01:54.583
They said you just need to rest.

01:01:56.958 --> 01:01:58.167
- What about the baby?

01:01:59.750 --> 01:02:00.833
- The baby's gonna be okay.

01:02:04.458 --> 01:02:05.666
What?

01:02:05.667 --> 01:02:08.000
Hey. Don't worry.
The baby's gonna be okay.

01:02:08.042 --> 01:02:10.291
You're gonna be fine.

01:02:10.292 --> 01:02:12.292
- I just thought it would
take care of itself.

01:02:16.375 --> 01:02:18.624
I just... I don't know
what I'm gonna do.

01:02:18.625 --> 01:02:21.375
- Hey, listen,
what we're gonna do.

01:02:21.417 --> 01:02:24.167
It's not just you any more.
It's us.

01:02:24.208 --> 01:02:25.667
Right?

01:02:25.708 --> 01:02:28.417
- Come on, Bobby.

01:02:28.458 --> 01:02:30.832
You don't want to have a kid.

01:02:30.833 --> 01:02:31.958
We barely know each other.

01:02:31.959 --> 01:02:34.291
I mean, you couldn't even
remember my name

01:02:34.292 --> 01:02:35.667
a few a days ago.

01:02:39.125 --> 01:02:41.499
- Is that what you think?

01:02:41.500 --> 01:02:44.625
That I couldn't remember
your name?

01:02:46.292 --> 01:02:48.417
You want to know the truth?

01:02:48.458 --> 01:02:51.333
- Yeah, the truth would be nice
for once.

01:02:53.417 --> 01:02:56.166
- Okay.

01:02:56.167 --> 01:02:59.332
Okay. Fine.

01:02:59.333 --> 01:03:01.166
After that night,

01:03:01.167 --> 01:03:05.333
I couldn't stop
thinking about you.

01:03:05.375 --> 01:03:08.417
I thought about you so much,
I was going nuts.

01:03:08.458 --> 01:03:09.958
I mean, I finally had you
out of my head,

01:03:09.959 --> 01:03:12.417
and then there you were
right in front of me.

01:03:14.750 --> 01:03:18.291
I got so nervous,
I couldn't even talk.

01:03:18.292 --> 01:03:19.667
- Why didn't you call me?

01:03:21.625 --> 01:03:24.333
- I was scared.

01:03:24.375 --> 01:03:27.500
When I woke up that morning,

01:03:27.542 --> 01:03:31.291
I looked over,
and you were so beautiful.

01:03:31.292 --> 01:03:35.166
You're so beautiful.

01:03:35.167 --> 01:03:38.499
First time
I didn't want to leave.

01:03:38.500 --> 01:03:41.708
That's never happened
to me before.

01:03:41.750 --> 01:03:43.417
I went to write down
my real number

01:03:43.458 --> 01:03:44.667
on a piece of paper,
and then I...

01:03:45.750 --> 01:03:46.833
I crumpled it up,

01:03:46.875 --> 01:03:48.167
and I wrote
a fake number instead.

01:03:48.208 --> 01:03:51.167
Then I... then I wrote
my real number down.

01:03:51.208 --> 01:03:53.000
I crumpled that up,
and, I don't know,

01:03:53.042 --> 01:03:55.375
I must have gone back and forth
and done that, like, ten times.

01:03:55.417 --> 01:03:57.542
And then I finally took all
the crumpled pieces of paper,

01:03:57.583 --> 01:03:58.790
and I put it in my pocket,

01:03:58.791 --> 01:04:00.000
and when I went to leave,

01:04:00.042 --> 01:04:01.750
I picked one out,
and I thought,

01:04:01.792 --> 01:04:03.165
"Hey, if this is
the real number,

01:04:03.166 --> 01:04:04.375
then it's meant to be."

01:04:06.125 --> 01:04:08.000
I kind of let fate decide,
you know?

01:04:10.375 --> 01:04:12.957
I know.

01:04:12.958 --> 01:04:14.957
I'm an asshole.

01:04:14.958 --> 01:04:16.083
It was stupid.

01:04:16.125 --> 01:04:18.083
I regretted it, but...

01:04:20.125 --> 01:04:23.042
I didn't forget your name, Lucy.

01:04:23.083 --> 01:04:24.542
I couldn't.

01:04:24.583 --> 01:04:26.500
I tried.
Believe me.

01:04:27.333 --> 01:04:29.292
- Why should I believe you?

01:04:41.000 --> 01:04:42.958
- I been carrying around that
for three months.

01:04:42.959 --> 01:04:45.957
I have problems
with commitment.

01:04:45.958 --> 01:04:48.250
- Yeah, I know.

01:04:48.292 --> 01:04:50.500
You can't even commit
to a brand of cigarettes.

01:04:54.708 --> 01:04:58.791
- I'm not gonna run away
from this, okay?

01:04:58.792 --> 01:05:00.125
That's my commitment to you.

01:05:01.792 --> 01:05:04.833
- I can't be with someone
who steals from people.

01:05:04.875 --> 01:05:05.917
- Then I'm done.

01:05:05.958 --> 01:05:08.333
I'll quit.

01:05:08.375 --> 01:05:10.750
Give me a chance, okay?
I'll prove it to you.

01:05:10.792 --> 01:05:12.624
Just give me a chance.

01:05:12.625 --> 01:05:13.917
- And you'll quit?

01:05:13.958 --> 01:05:16.208
You can quit just like that'?

01:05:16.250 --> 01:05:18.000
For me?

01:05:23.583 --> 01:05:25.833
Okay.

01:05:32.958 --> 01:05:34.833
- Hey, hey, you guys.

01:05:34.875 --> 01:05:36.124
Get a room.

01:05:36.125 --> 01:05:39.958
Visiting hours are over,
and you need your rest.

01:07:53.917 --> 01:07:55.833
- You're in with the cops, Jax?

01:08:00.667 --> 01:08:03.000
You're in with the cops?
You?

01:08:03.042 --> 01:08:04.457
- Shut up!

01:08:04.458 --> 01:08:05.665
I should kill you right now.

01:08:05.666 --> 01:08:07.542
- Why would you sell me out
like that?

01:08:07.583 --> 01:08:08.875
- We ain't friends!

01:08:08.917 --> 01:08:10.667
- I gave up my life, Jax!

01:08:10.708 --> 01:08:12.583
Leave up my life!

01:08:12.625 --> 01:08:14.291
- We are not friends!

01:08:14.292 --> 01:08:16.707
Don't mess with my business!

01:08:18.250 --> 01:08:20.957
Steal a cop's badge?

01:08:24.292 --> 01:08:27.124
Those cops came barging
into my house!

01:08:27.125 --> 01:08:28.624
My house!

01:08:28.625 --> 01:08:29.792
- You work for me now.

01:08:30.875 --> 01:08:32.667
What, is that
supposed to be funny?

01:08:32.707 --> 01:08:34.999
I told them where you live.

01:08:35.000 --> 01:08:38.000
I told them where you'd be
and when you'd be there.

01:08:38.042 --> 01:08:39.332
- You had that guy
steal my money.

01:08:39.375 --> 01:08:40.624
- Yeah, I did.

01:08:40.625 --> 01:08:42.250
I figured you'd have
some money on you.

01:08:42.292 --> 01:08:43.332
Mr. Morality.

01:08:43.375 --> 01:08:46.166
He's gotta pay for all that shit
with his girlfriend.

01:08:46.167 --> 01:08:47.667
She couldn't chip in nothing.

01:08:47.707 --> 01:08:50.375
That friend did me a favor.

01:08:50.417 --> 01:08:51.707
That friend ratted me out.

01:08:52.707 --> 01:08:54.124
- Give me a name!

01:08:54.125 --> 01:08:55.375
- Jax.

01:08:55.417 --> 01:08:56.957
- Did I get mad at him?

01:08:56.957 --> 01:08:58.707
No.

01:08:58.750 --> 01:09:01.124
You know why?

01:09:01.125 --> 01:09:03.125
Because it's business, Bobby.

01:09:03.167 --> 01:09:04.917
Business.

01:09:04.957 --> 01:09:06.457
It's not personal.

01:09:10.957 --> 01:09:13.042
It's over.

01:09:17.707 --> 01:09:19.457
- Wait.
Wait.

01:09:19.457 --> 01:09:20.457
Listen.

01:09:20.457 --> 01:09:21.456
- Detective Sullivan.

01:09:21.457 --> 01:09:22.956
- What if I could get you
your 50 grand back

01:09:22.957 --> 01:09:23.957
and everything I owe you?

01:09:23.959 --> 01:09:25.666
- It's too late.

01:09:25.667 --> 01:09:27.542
Okay, okay, you know what?
Call the cops.

01:09:27.582 --> 01:09:28.790
Call the cops, Jax.

01:09:28.791 --> 01:09:29.790
They got nothing on me.

01:09:29.791 --> 01:09:30.956
Look, I don't have the badge.

01:09:30.957 --> 01:09:33.125
You and I both know, without
that badge they got nothing.

01:09:33.126 --> 01:09:35.124
- Lock the door!
- Nothing.

01:09:35.125 --> 01:09:36.082
- This game is over now.

01:09:36.125 --> 01:09:39.125
- I got a score we could pull
that'll get you so much money,

01:09:39.167 --> 01:09:40.625
you won't have to
nickel... and... dime any more.

01:09:42.792 --> 01:09:45.500
You like diamonds?

01:09:45.542 --> 01:09:46.917
- I'm listening.

01:09:46.957 --> 01:09:48.624
It better be good.

01:09:48.625 --> 01:09:50.000
- I'm gonna get you
some diamonds.

01:09:55.792 --> 01:09:58.499
- Bobby?
- Oh, hey.

01:09:58.500 --> 01:10:01.332
- Hi.

01:10:01.333 --> 01:10:03.042
- How you feeling?

01:10:03.083 --> 01:10:05.208
- I'm a lot better.

01:10:05.250 --> 01:10:07.666
They said I can probably
go home this afternoon.

01:10:07.667 --> 01:10:08.875
You know, they're just waiting

01:10:08.917 --> 01:10:12.458
on a few more test results
to make sure.

01:10:12.500 --> 01:10:14.208
You okay?

01:10:14.250 --> 01:10:16.792
- Yeah, yeah, I'm fine.

01:10:19.792 --> 01:10:20.750
- Are those for me?

01:10:20.792 --> 01:10:22.667
- Oh, yeah.

01:10:22.708 --> 01:10:24.542
Sorry.
- Thank you.

01:10:29.792 --> 01:10:32.333
- Listen, Lucy,
I know I said yesterday

01:10:32.375 --> 01:10:34.167
that I could quit, but...

01:10:35.792 --> 01:10:37.000
Well, something kind of came up,

01:10:37.042 --> 01:10:40.375
and I got to do this...
this one last thing.

01:10:41.750 --> 01:10:43.292
- What are you talking about?

01:10:45.625 --> 01:10:49.333
- It's just... it's just
a little complicated.

01:10:49.375 --> 01:10:51.124
I just need you to trust me.

01:10:51.125 --> 01:10:52.750
I mean, the whole reason
why I'm telling you any of this

01:10:52.792 --> 01:10:54.791
is because I want to be honest
with you.

01:10:54.792 --> 01:10:56.208
- Be honest with me?

01:10:56.250 --> 01:10:58.250
You haven't told me anything.

01:10:58.292 --> 01:10:59.250
- I know.

01:10:59.292 --> 01:11:01.750
I... look, I can't.

01:11:01.792 --> 01:11:03.583
I wish I could, but...

01:11:04.958 --> 01:11:08.750
- You try to run,
or you tell anybody,

01:11:08.792 --> 01:11:11.708
and I swear to God,
I'll fucking kill you,

01:11:11.750 --> 01:11:13.124
and I'll kill her.

01:11:13.125 --> 01:11:14.124
- I swear.

01:11:14.125 --> 01:11:16.083
After tomorrow,
it'll all be over.

01:11:16.125 --> 01:11:17.624
I'll be done.

01:11:17.625 --> 01:11:18.917
- Well, I won't be here
tomorrow.

01:11:18.958 --> 01:11:20.083
I'm getting on a plane,
remember?

01:11:22.625 --> 01:11:23.625
- Just give me the day.

01:11:23.667 --> 01:11:26.083
Okay?

01:11:26.125 --> 01:11:27.583
I'll explain everything.

01:11:39.625 --> 01:11:40.917
I love you.

01:11:55.958 --> 01:11:57.666
Hey, Carl.

01:11:57.667 --> 01:11:59.999
It... it's Bobby.

01:12:00.000 --> 01:12:01.958
Listen, I need a favor.

01:12:04.792 --> 01:12:06.957
- We're closed.

01:12:06.958 --> 01:12:08.875
- I'm Bobby's friend.

01:12:08.917 --> 01:12:11.000
- Oh, yeah, sure.

01:12:15.375 --> 01:12:17.042
Yeah, Bobby mentioned
you were gonna come.

01:12:17.083 --> 01:12:18.042
Come on in.
I'm Carl.

01:12:18.083 --> 01:12:19.042
- You're Carl?
- Yeah.

01:12:19.083 --> 01:12:20.708
- I'm Dennis.
- Hey, Dennis.

01:12:20.750 --> 01:12:21.875
- I'm really sorry I'm late.

01:12:21.917 --> 01:12:22.875
I just got off work.

01:12:22.917 --> 01:12:24.167
- No, that's okay.

01:12:24.208 --> 01:12:28.542
So Bobby tells me you work
on Wall Street together, huh?

01:12:28.583 --> 01:12:30.291
- No, no.

01:12:30.292 --> 01:12:31.457
I'm his boss.

01:12:31.458 --> 01:12:34.500
- Oh, and, you're looking
for an engagement ring, right?

01:12:34.542 --> 01:12:37.125
- Yeah.

01:12:37.167 --> 01:12:38.292
- I'm gonna tell you the truth.

01:12:38.333 --> 01:12:39.833
I know nothing about jewelry.

01:12:39.875 --> 01:12:40.833
I mean, really nothing.

01:12:40.875 --> 01:12:41.833
I don't wear anything.

01:12:41.875 --> 01:12:43.333
- I won't hold that against you.

01:12:43.375 --> 01:12:46.833
But my fiancée
has very expensive taste,

01:12:46.875 --> 01:12:48.290
and I want to get her something
really nice.

01:12:48.291 --> 01:12:49.500
- How much you lookin' to spend?

01:12:49.542 --> 01:12:53.124
- I'm looking to spend
about $30,000,

01:12:53.125 --> 01:12:54.956
if I can get something nice
for that.

01:12:54.957 --> 01:12:56.250
- $30,000.
- That would be great.

01:12:56.292 --> 01:12:57.250
- Yeah.

01:12:57.292 --> 01:12:58.667
You... you must be doing
very well.

01:12:58.668 --> 01:13:00.083
- I get by, yeah.

01:13:00.125 --> 01:13:04.542
- All right,
let me bring something out.

01:13:04.583 --> 01:13:07.291
These are all 21/2 to 3 karats.

01:13:07.292 --> 01:13:12.457
They're VVS1 and 2s
and pretty much all J color.

01:13:12.458 --> 01:13:13.667
- That's not an engagement ring,
is it?

01:13:13.708 --> 01:13:14.667
- Yeah, it is.

01:13:14.708 --> 01:13:17.250
If there's a diamond in here
that you like,

01:13:17.292 --> 01:13:18.542
but you don't like the setting,

01:13:18.583 --> 01:13:21.332
something like her grandmother
has a ring that she used,

01:13:21.333 --> 01:13:23.208
and she wants to put
the diamond in it...

01:13:23.250 --> 01:13:26.208
Do you know what style
she might prefer?

01:13:26.250 --> 01:13:28.292
- Everything about
getting married is so stressful.

01:13:28.333 --> 01:13:31.417
I thought... I thought an
engagement ring was one style.

01:13:31.458 --> 01:13:33.665
I didn't know there were
so many different styles.

01:13:33.666 --> 01:13:36.000
- Why don't you fish around
a little bit more, you know?

01:13:36.001 --> 01:13:38.457
Go around with her
maybe this weekend,

01:13:38.458 --> 01:13:39.458
and when you see something

01:13:39.500 --> 01:13:41.000
or she sees something
that she likes,

01:13:41.001 --> 01:13:43.000
then you guys
can come back here.

01:13:43.042 --> 01:13:45.500
- I got a bunch of people
at my house tonight,

01:13:45.542 --> 01:13:49.875
and I was hoping, really hoping,
to bring something for her.

01:13:49.917 --> 01:13:50.875
You know, I got food there.

01:13:50.917 --> 01:13:52.042
We're having a whole big party.

01:13:52.083 --> 01:13:53.458
- I can't bring all of this.

01:13:53.459 --> 01:13:55.832
- I have a simple idea.

01:13:55.833 --> 01:13:56.832
I got $15,000.

01:13:56.833 --> 01:13:58.083
- It's not about the money.

01:13:58.125 --> 01:13:59.417
- No, no, no.
Just listen.

01:13:59.458 --> 01:14:01.000
Listen to what I'm gonna say.

01:14:01.042 --> 01:14:03.124
Let me give you a deposit.

01:14:03.125 --> 01:14:04.708
We take a bunch of rings,

01:14:04.750 --> 01:14:06.833
whichever ones
you think she'll like.

01:14:06.875 --> 01:14:07.917
We bring them over there.

01:14:07.958 --> 01:14:08.917
I'm two minutes away.

01:14:08.958 --> 01:14:10.000
- Dennis, I'm trying to be...

01:14:10.042 --> 01:14:11.583
you know, I know
you're Bobby's friend.

01:14:11.625 --> 01:14:12.583
- Whatever one she likes,

01:14:12.625 --> 01:14:14.500
as long as we're
in that range of price,

01:14:14.542 --> 01:14:16.290
I'll pay you the balance in cash
right there.

01:14:16.291 --> 01:14:17.833
- You're talking...
there's over...

01:14:17.875 --> 01:14:19.333
